{"tid":1752821,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"怎麼才算贏建制派?","createTime":"2019-11-24T23:55:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T04:38:09.000Z","uid":247610,"like":53,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"6eab1c63d883093fe91396ad58295a5333d94342","tid":1752821,"uid":247610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T23:55:56.000Z","msg":"1.要在建制派顛峰期定勝負 <br />\n2.要在建制派內部沒有矛盾的時候選 <br />\n3.要在民建聯最多人支持的時候選 <br />\n4.你不能鬧建制候選人<br />\n5.你不能支持民主<br />\n6.你不能在日落前投票，要讓公公婆婆先投 <br />\n7.你不能壓迫式抹黑，要給建制派足夠的空間發揮 <br />\n8.你不能支持港獨 <br />\n9.選管會要偏向親中，最好一開始就DQ非建制候選人 <br />\n10.建制義工洗樓時，你不能幾個人去攔截，要讓義工順利派掌心雷 <br />\n11.你不能一邊錄影一邊問建制候選人問題 <br />\n12.你的票數要高過建制候選人10倍，這樣才是真水平，否則建制認為是靠運氣 <br />\n13.你要在沉默大多數完全醒覺時進行選舉<br />\n14.你要允許建制候選人在點票時與選舉主任交流 <br />\n15.務必遵守以上守則，否則即使你不小心贏了，建制派也會說你是勝之不武，說你是靠運氣，說你無恥。建制派總是可以找到一條理由來說明你不應該贏區選。"},{"pid":"25f8894513d46e49d9d64f2c59e7f5e7301c5864","tid":1752821,"uid":122566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T00:05:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc96461a87e362734f360c9435c0860a99dbb639","tid":1752821,"uid":33437,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T00:07:27.000Z","msg":"所以我地係咩都無勝到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n五大訴求，<br />\n缺一不可。"},{"pid":"21bf2d2fb109a0610ab2b702f689ba88ea2b848e","tid":1752821,"uid":235465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T00:11:21.000Z","msg":"[核彈]搵到建制派春袋,唔想輸同我入黎推爆佢"},{"pid":"931a58c441179d0ea44a6364867c4df32652b0ca","tid":1752821,"uid":247610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dc96461a87e362734f360c9435c0860a99dbb639","tid":1752821,"uid":33437,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T00:07:27.000Z","msg":"所以我地係咩都無勝到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n五大訴求，<br />\n缺一不可。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T00:19:38.000Z","msg":"今次唔計"},{"pid":"3091a4a78758c035abddd02acd3be01efb59ead3","tid":1752821,"uid":47135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T00:23:20.000Z","msg":"今次唔計啦"},{"pid":"2a8166bb7bdfa0e26e39b8ad561e48f893f05d8b","tid":1752821,"uid":35585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T00:24:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/pig_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/pig_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3db5345abf2ddc01a9d018d5134abe584c938ff","tid":1752821,"uid":23140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T00:56:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f541cdd06059a263bb7fb252c18e912e711bd6b","tid":1752821,"uid":226233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T02:34:22.000Z","msg":"全民投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"add82c00f1a0bca934dd00a31ef733878c073326","tid":1752821,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T04:19:18.000Z","msg":"俾昵吳秋得睇下"},{"pid":"53d89f822572e1943a04bae6c0307b342f924546","tid":1752821,"uid":28252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T04:23:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dcc067e1cf34462b9d24fa396af5c0a0c7c2235e","tid":1752821,"uid":247610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f541cdd06059a263bb7fb252c18e912e711bd6b","tid":1752821,"uid":226233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T02:34:22.000Z","msg":"全民投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hk